      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it currently starts, it suffers from several mechanical issues, including a rough idle and a noticeable transmission slip. The exterior has substantial body damage, including rusted panels and multiple large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts.",
