    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you may find some minor rock chips and very light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. The interior is in great shape, with no tears in the upholstery and all electronic features functioning perfectly. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
