      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in this wonderful and reliable vehicle! It's in good condition, showing it has been well-maintained and is ready for its next chapter. While you might find a few minor signs of its previous adventures, it performs beautifully and offers a smooth, dependable ride. This is a fantastic opportunity to own a quality car that still has so much to give!",
