      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next adventure. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with regular maintenance so it\u2019s ready to hit the road the moment you get the keys. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great in the driveway, this is definitely the one for you! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 996.2 Carrera, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This unit delivers linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal (RMS) is dry. Recent borescope inspection confirms clean cylinder walls with no sign of scoring. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are impeccable. A true enthusiast\u2019s 911 maintained for the apex, not the showroom.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Reliable engine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
